{"tid":7771,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"靴里拉：不知道如何獲勝","createTime":"2016-11-28T03:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T17:49:02.000Z","uid":4082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9eae638d30288b6bd24c24311021211c238bc7","tid":7771,"uid":4082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=l2m5Ikuj4XgffAL1vfCQXsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=cf1631bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯周日主場迎戰韋斯咸，只能與對手握手言和1:1，聯賽主場4連和，中場安達靴里拉慨嘆贏形勢卻不勝。<br />\n<br />\n由於多支前列球隊報捷，曼聯失掉兩分後續排第6位，但落後榜首差距多達11分，中場安達靴里拉（Ander Herrera）賽後嘆道：「如出一轍的局面，我們由開波到終場都控制大局，韋斯咸憑一記幸運入波打開紀錄。」<br />\n<br />\n「對史篤城、般尼和阿仙奴，再到今日的韋斯咸，對手門將又是比賽最佳，我們真不知道要如何獲勝。」靴里拉也感茫然：「足球是講求入波的比賽，目前我們做不到，這是事實。」<br />\n<br />\n領隊摩連奴在上半場因激動踢水樽被罰上看台，助教法利亞賽後表示：「己隊表現出色，已用盡辦法取勝，並踢出了部署，正如之前欠運的比賽，差一點已經會得出截然的賽果。然而，我們相信想看見的賽果將會出現。」"},{"pid":"03a17e9b3a8d93803692bcd510be6fbb6f56f9b0","tid":7771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"3d315fc104575ef5523626495dcf3811e9c5ddd3","tid":7771,"uid":2770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"韋斯咸憑一記幸運入波打開紀錄<br />\n<br />\n幸你老母咩幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e397a20d428b3759957c5865631749efac69c96","tid":7771,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"諗起椰子好似講過類似野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d12af237d3c8eb3de21fc81abf701c9fcc2d99","tid":7771,"uid":32181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"全世界逼害daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7618be1110a72efeef9be78941f1cd08b8bc096","tid":7771,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韋斯咸憑一記幸運入波打開紀錄<br />\n<br />\n幸你老母咩幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獌狗真係好撚弱智，人地入波就話幸運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4865c4ff6a77df6a732f6896a61c2a8d4ab3dd","tid":7771,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>韋斯咸憑一記幸運入波打開紀錄<br />\n<br />\n幸你老母咩幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獌狗真係好撚弱智，人地入波就話幸運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢自己果球都係普巴大斬比廢老😂"},{"pid":"d701cbaeebf92a29b077e3dbbd899da763d547a3","tid":7771,"uid":7431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起椰子好似講過類似野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n證明左咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a969da194bc0004b5f574fd7da2b651b731943","tid":7771,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"換咗領隊就得<br />\n<br />\n摩狗我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000b7abf0d0a4531c0b618e6f714a0b23e20ffff","tid":7771,"uid":10693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"史篤城、般尼和阿仙奴，再到今日的韋斯咸，對手門將又是比賽最佳<br />\n<br />\n所有門將夾份迫害曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db99fccccbad61c32117954efccfe3f1a2fb0c1d","tid":7771,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"人地入就係幸運 自己入唔到就係唔幸運<br />\n姐係場場都係踢緊-6足球"},{"pid":"38c34b816b6d5548abd2688f925da8b8e18b2